        <font color="white" face="Verdana" size="2"> I have been trying to better familiarize myself with my spells by reading the spdat, and I have a few questions about how exactly a few things work. </P><P><BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=2 face="Verdana" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote><BR>Cascading Darkness<BR>Resistance Check: Magic<BR>Spell Duration: 16 ticks (1.6 minutes)<BR>Duration Formula: 1</P><P>Dooming Darkness<BR>Resistance Check: Magic + 25<BR>Spell Duration: 15 ticks (1.5 minutes)<BR>Duration Formula: 1</P><P>Fear<BR>Resistance Check: Magic + 25<BR>Spell Duration: 3 ticks (18 seconds)<BR>Duration Formula: 7<BR><hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana" size=2 id=quote></P><P>First question is which is resisted more often Magic+25, or Magic? Is the number added a bonus or a penalty to teh resistance check?</P><P>Next is the duration formula. Does anyone know what these numbers mean? Is that the numer of point of dispelling/curing it takes to remove the spell? Is higher better than lower?</P><P><BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=2 face="Verdana" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote><BR>Dominate Undead<BR>Attempting to charm (1)<BR>Resistance Check: Magic+25</P><P>Beguile Undead<BR>Attempting to charm (9)<BR>Resistance Check: Magic+25</P><P>Cajole Undead<BR>Attempting to charm (16)<BR>Resistance Check: Magic</P><P>Thrall of Bones<BR>Attempting to charm (16)<BR>Resistance Check: Magic<BR><hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana" size=2 id=quote></P><P>These spells are levels 16, 34, 49, and 54. Does anyone know what the number in parenthese means? Does it affect what level you can charm? I also noticed the 2 low spells have same resistance check, and teh 2 high ones also share the same resistance check. Seem one should work better than the other. Anyone have any ideas about that?</P><P></P><P><a target="new"  href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=117251">Talanor S`Tox</a><BR>Necromancer of Innoruuk</P><P><a target="new" href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=116028">Tazuuk</a><BR>Necromancer of Cazic Thule<BR></font></td>

